Package: dhw
Title: A Package for Calculating Degree Heating Weeks and other SST Metrics
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Roff", , "george.roff@csiro.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates various SST metrics (Degree Heating Weeks, SST Anomalies, HotSpots, Mean Monthly Maximum) from daily SST sources following the NOAA Coral Reef Watch (CRW) methodology (https://coralreefwatch.noaa.gov for details)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
